{% comment %}
  Testimonials Section
{% endcomment %}

<section class="testimonials-section" id="testimonials">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header fade-in">
            <span class="section-eyebrow">Customer Reviews</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">Trusted by Thousands</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonials-grid">
            <div class="testimonial-card fade-in">
                <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testimonial-text">"When I use too much of the most used commercial laundry detergent, I feel my clothes are too stiff. With Love Paks, I could feel the difference, my clothes are really soft and I didn't use softener."</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <span class="testimonial-name">Claudia R.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card fade-in">
                <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testimonial-text">"After using Love Paks for a month, I noticed that I was sleeping better, I didn't feel as anxious and in general I was feeling more at peace with myself and connected with the world around me."</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <span class="testimonial-name">Ryan H.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card fade-in">
                <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testimonial-text">"Ever since I can remember, I had the Restless Leg Syndrome, I've been using Love Paks for about two months and now I can tell the difference. My mind is more at ease, and I barely find myself moving my legs."</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <span class="testimonial-name">Katherinne L.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card fade-in">
                <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testimonial-text">"A friend of mine, who is way more into wellness products than I am, gifted me a pouch of Love Paks, and I don't know how to explain it, but I've been feeling calmer and more capable to deal with daily routine."</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <span class="testimonial-name">Daniela A.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card fade-in">
                <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testimonial-text">"I won't say this product cured my anxiety, but ever since I've been using it, I've had less anxiety attacks, I feel with more strength and calm to go through the day."</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <span class="testimonial-name">William P.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card fade-in">
                <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testimonial-text">"When it's laundry day my entire apartment smells amazing, I use the Citrus Blossom version."</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <span class="testimonial-name">Julieth S.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card testimonial-hidden fade-in">
                <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testimonial-text">"This product makes me smile every time I have to do laundry. From the packaging design, the amazing scent, and the unique rose quartz aspect, you can tell a lot of love has gone into making this product."</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <span class="testimonial-name">Courtney S.</span>
                    <span class="testimonial-location">Wisconsin</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card testimonial-hidden fade-in">
                <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testimonial-text">"I love this product soooo much, I was sad when I ran out!"</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <span class="testimonial-name">Brooke E.</span>
                    <span class="testimonial-location">Wisconsin</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card testimonial-hidden fade-in">
                <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testimonial-text">"The feeling was subtle at first, but after a week or so of use, we could tell our entire family seemed to be more energetically aligned."</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <span class="testimonial-name">Nikki and Luke</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Load More Button -->
        <div class="testimonials-load-more-wrapper">
            <button class="btn-secondary testimonials-load-more-btn" id="testimonials-load-more">
                Load More Reviews
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

